The Mercedes CLR GTR had significant success in sports car racing, particularly in the FIA GT Championship. - It achieved multiple race wins and podium finishes, showcasing its performance and competitiveness on the track. A dummy model of the Chinook helicopter prepared by the Defense Research and Development Organisation (DRDO) for the purpose of displaying it at the 2020 Defence Expo has now been reported stolen. The exhibition was held in Lucknow, the capital of Uttar Pradesh state. The replica became a popular spot during the expo as people flocked to take selfies of the life-sized structure.
